name: WNRS videogame
description:
Do you want to meet or know more about someone? Or instead do you want to go deeper with some of your friends?

This is a FAN GAME based on the famous card game We're Not Really Strangers, where you will be able to deepen your actuals relationships or create new ones through different levels of questions.

Go and start to ask!

♦ Game completely developed by: https://twitter.com/keyday_16
